            <title>[SPARK-40480] Remove push-based shuffle data after query finished</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-40480</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Now spark will only cleanup shuffle data files except push-based shuffle files.&lt;br/&gt;
In our production cluster, push-based shuffle service will create too many shuffle merge data files as there are several spark thrift server.&lt;br/&gt;
Could we cleanup the merged data files after the query finished?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
